                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/phpstorm/edit/master/knpu/forms.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Now that we've got our entity let's create a form! Click on AppBundle, press our handy
shortcut <code>command+n</code>, and if you search form you'll find that option in the menu!
It's all coming together!</p>
<p>We'll call this <code>MovieType</code>:</p>
