</p>
<p>Notice it was actually smart enough to put that inside of a <code>Form</code> directory <em>and</em>
build out the whole structure that we'll need. All I need next is for it to pour me
a cup of coffee.</p>
<p>The first thing we always do inside of here is call <code>$resolver-&gt;setDefaults(array())</code>
and pass the <code>data_class</code> option so that it binds it to our <code>Movie</code> entity. Conveniently,
this gives us more autocomplete: we can just type <code>Movie</code> and it adds the rest:</p>
